    13484,"Trapped in the treacherous swamps by two of the cruelest forces of the jungle ...", 830,"Anitra rescues Kanga from yet another attack by Sam Broot and his men but when Kanga refuses to become her king she prepares to sacrifice him.  Ann and Cheba arrive and prevent the execution and Anitra allows Kanga to go free because of his love for Ann.  Later however Anitra dispatches her men to kidnap Ann and feed her to the crocodiles.  Kanga manages to rescue Ann at the last second and once again delivers a pasting to Sam Broot.",NULL,NULL,19);
